{"tid":1185864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★德意志(DWS)警告若中美貿易戰惡化　恒指將跌10至15%","createTime":"2019-06-04T13:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T06:32:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"41296101f8107cb88587daeeb1a90eab3d1e14ef","tid":1185864,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:55:18.000Z","msg":"德意志財富管理發布下半年投資展望，預料內地今明兩年經濟增長成功「保六」，而美國明年的增幅將會放緩，至2%；又預料美國年底前減息機會很微。若中美貿易戰惡化，恒生指數或跌10至15%。<br />\n<br />\n若貿易戰惡化 港股將跌10至15%<br />\n<br />\n德意志財富管理亞太區投資主管Sean Taylor表示，中美貿易戰持續，其所帶來的影響已於股價中反映，若未來保持現狀，股市相信都可維持。若情況惡化，預期港股會下跌10至15%。他建議投資者採取防守策略，購買內需股、教育、旅遊及電子商務等股票，而他對美股的看法則有所保留。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4/336798/dws%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E8%8B%A5%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E6%83%A1%E5%8C%96-%E6%81%92%E6%8C%87%E5%B0%87%E8%B7%8C10%E8%87%B315-%E9%A0%90%E6%96%99%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E6%B8%9B%E6%81%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%2F336798%2Fdws%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%258B%25A5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%2583%25A1%25E5%258C%2596-%25E6%2581%2592%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%25B7%258C10%25E8%2587%25B315-%25E9%25A0%2590%25E6%2596%2599%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25B8%259B%25E6%2581%25AF&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9Cgvhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=52f3adaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4/336798/dws%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E8%8B%A5%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E6%83%A1%E5%8C%96-%E6%81%92%E6%8C%87%E5%B0%87%E8%B7%8C10%E8%87%B315-%E9%A0%90%E6%96%99%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E6%B8%9B%E6%81%AF</a>"},{"pid":"60438c01fddcf0238c8c3831c53da1bed7ee43fa","tid":1185864,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:55:2